HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(20): How do I connect my Shapa and app?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(21): Shapa connects via bluetooth to the app. Make sure you have bluetooth enabled on your smartphone. Once you open the app and step on your Shapa, Shapa will connect with the app.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(23): Shapa syncs with app via Bluetooth (the light behind the S on the scale will turn blue when the app and scale are syncing). Try turning the bluetooth ‘off’ and then back ‘on’ again on your phone, then step back up on your Shapa.  Don’t hesitate to reach out, we’re here to help - send us an email at shapahealth@shapa.me or give us a call (408) 207-5201.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(24): Can I sync my Shapa with other applications or devices?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(25): The Shapa scale syncs with the Shapa app on your smartphone. You can connect Shapa with Apple Health to give Shapa access to additional information likes steps, activity, heart rate and more. The Shapa app will be connected to GoogleFit soon.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(26): I don’t have a smartphone. Can I still use Shapa?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(27): The personalized program is only available on a smartphone. You can order a scale and take the questionnaire online at www.shapa.me but you won’t have access to your personalized program without a smartphone.

HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(31): Shapa syncs with app via Bluetooth (the light behind the S on the scale will turn blue when the app and scale are syncing). Try turning the bluetooth ‘off’ and then back ‘on’ again on your phone, then step back up on your Shapa.  Don’t hesitate to reach out, we’re here to help - send us an email at shapahealth@shapa.me or give us a call (408) 207-5201.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(32): Can I sync my Shapa with other applications or devices?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(33): The Shapa scale syncs with the Shapa app on your smartphone. You can connect Shapa with Apple Health to give Shapa access to additional information likes steps, activity, heart rate and more. The Shapa app will be connected to GoogleFit soon.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(34): I don’t have a smartphone. Can I still use Shapa?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(35): The personalized program is only available on a smartphone. You can order a scale and take the questionnaire online at www.shapa.me but you won’t have access to your personalized program without a smartphone.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(36): What is the purpose of the questionnaire that Shapa is asking me to complete?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(37): The Shapa questionnaire helps Shapa get to know you - your habits, personality, and lifestyle. Your responses on the questionnaire help Shapa to build your customized program of missions.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(38): How do I choose which day of the week to start?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(39): The best day to start is today.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(40): How often should I use Shapa for best results?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(41): We recommend stepping on your Shapa twice a day, ideally in the morning and the evening, for the best results. In the app you can set reminders for yourself to step up on your Shapa twice daily.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(42): Where do my missions go after I complete them?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(43): Shapa keeps track of your progress on your missions and will suggest new missions based on your responses in the questionnaire and the type of missions that has been successful for you. Shapa is constantly learning about you and adjusting your program as you complete missions and step on your Shapa scale. To help you stay on track you can add a reminder to complete your mission to your calendar.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(44): How does Shapa figure out my goals?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(45): When you first join Shapa you are asked to fill out a questionnaire. Shapa uses your responses in the questionnaire to learn about your personality, hobbies and lifestyle, and environment. From there Shapa selects activities that we think would fit best into your daily life.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(47): You can update your responses to the questionnaire at any time by logging into your account on the Shapa website. Shapa will adjust your program based on your new responses. You can also update what you feel is your ideal weight and age in the app by clicking on Settings and Ideal Age & Weight.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(48): Will my goals change as I progress?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(49): Shapa will continue to suggest and adjust activities for you based on your personality, habits, and environment. You’ll also notice changes in your Shapa Color and Age as you progress towards long-term weight management and a healthy lifestyle to give you feedback and motivate you.

HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(65): Shapa is intended to give you more clear and consistent feedback about how you are doing on your health journey within your body’s natural fluctuations. After a few weeks of using Shapa, you can choose to unlock your Weight History under Progress Review in the app. If you choose to unlock your Weight History, Shapa will show you your starting weight (based on an average of your first 10 measurements) and your current weight (based on an average of your most recent 10 measurements).
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(67): Your Shapa Age is a truer metric of your health. It takes into account your body’s natural fluctuations in weight as well as other health metrics to provide you a health age. Your Shapa Age gives you feedback on your progress over the course of your Shapa journey.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(69): The Shapa Color is a 5-point scale which gives you feedback each time you step on your Shapa scale. Your Shapa Color will give your feedback on your weight trend over the past 3 weeks so you can track your weight progress in a meaningful way.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(70): Can I view my total progress in the app?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(71): Your Shapa Age will give you feedback on your overall progress in the program. You can also view your Weigh-In History and Mission History in the app to see how far you’ve come in your Shapa program.

HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(84): How do I change my profile information?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(85): Click on the Settings or hamburger icon (three horizontal lines) in the app to change your profile information. It's located in the top left corner of your Shapa dashboard (the main screen in the app).
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(86): Can I share my profile with my friends?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(87): Currently Shapa is a personal journey, but feel free to share your progress with your friends. If you have suggestions for features you would like to see on Shapa, drop us a line at shapahealth@shapa.me.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(88): Where can I find my license key?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(89): After you have placed your order for a Shapa scale and subscription you will receive an email from Shapa with your unique license key included.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(90): What is the purpose of the license key?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(91): Shapa generates unique license keys for every paid Shapa subscription. You will need this license key to link your Shapa account with your subscription.
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(92): Where do I enter the license key?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(93): In the email that contains your license key, there is a direct link that will automatically enters the license key for you.. Alternatively, you can also type in your license key directly into the app when prompted.

HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(108): Can more than one person share one Shapa?
HelpScreen.ObjectProperty.index(109): Yes, up to 7 people can use one Shapa. For example, you can buy one Shapa for your whole family. Each user should set up his or her own profile. Each family member should enter the license key or confirmation code the primary account holder received when creating their account. Pro tip: when you step on your shared Shapa, make sure your app is open and other family members have their app closed. This will make sure Shapa knows who is stepping on it.
